[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/shadow_ball">Shadow Ball</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/shadow_ball">Shadow Ball</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user hurls a shadowy blob at the foe. It may also lower the foe's SpD one stage.</p>